profile: I am an Interior Decorator who specializes in Paint Colour Consulting and Home Decor.  I am Dewey Colour Certified and have a certificate in interior design.  I have used my colour expertise to help numerous satisfied customers with their in-home and exterior colour selections and specialize in the Benjamin Moore colour palette.  I am also experienced in the Para and Pratt & Lambert colour palettes
diplomas: Certificate In Interior Design and Dewey Colour Certified,
